name: Brian Doyle-Murray
summary: Brian Doyle-Murray. Actor: Caddyshack. Brian Doyle-Murray was born on 31 October 1945 in Chicago, Illinois, USA. He is an actor and writer, known for Caddyshack (1980), JFK (1991) and Groundhog Day (1993). He has been married to Christina Stauffer since 28 August 2000.
